Metadata: The ecology of "Crassostrea gigas" in Australia, New Zealand, France and Washington State

The following papers are included in this publication: 1. Introduced Pacific oysters in Australia. Peter Ayres pp. 3-8. 2. Introduced Pacific oysters in New Zealand. Parameswar Dinimani pp. 9-12. 3. Aquaculture of "Crassostrea gigas" in France. Philippe Goulletquer and Maurice Heral pp. 13-20. 4. Ecological and biological considerations for the introduced Pacific oyster on the west coast of the United States. Kenneth K. Chew pp. 21-24.
